{
  "stem": "1603.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was a young man then.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And mater of fact, he helped me with my homework as a school student.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And his hobby was, he bought himself an 8 millimeter camera, and on the weekends he would go out and make shots with this little 8 millimeter camera.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that was his hobby.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then the war came, and we got parted and separated and everything.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And when I was in America, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] many, many, many years later, I was reading magazine that from Czechoslovakia, Jan Kadar is-- is-- how would you say-- he was up for an Oscar award as a director for a motion picture made in Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I said to myself, that must be Jan.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I called Prague Information immediately.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I found him, and that was him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we got together with Jan.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- but I just wonder how did he come into my conversation now?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's why I'm telling you this, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was asking you about the people in the building, in the bakery.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yes, yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "OK, thank you.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Jan Kadar was a true artist.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And nobody could buy him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in America, as an Oscar-winning director, he got many offers, and he refused most of the offers he got.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he took one job where Mohammad Ali was-- was playing, and it called It was a television movie and-- and he made it-- Jan made it.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he directed it, Jan Kadar directed it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he told me, he said, at the end of this movie, there are many black kids there hiding from the whites.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
